(9,49,'<p><img id=\"blog_image_63\" class=\"center img-responsive\" src=\"/tt/tt.php?src=./uploads/hn4.jpg&amp;w=940&amp;h=\" alt=\"\" />The band Human Nature, originally from West Sussex, will be hitting up a close circle of friends in south London this time next week with their premiere live performance and we can\'t help ourselves but be rooting and tooting over this imminent epochal moment. &nbsp;Here are some quick shots of the band and a quick promo video we threw together based on some rehearsal vibes that went down a couple of weeks ago, just as we entered the new year, from the band\'s newly established fucking sweet jam zone.</p>\r\n<p>Look out for more from these guys soon.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"embed-responsive embed-responsive-16by9\"><iframe src=\"//www.youtube.com/embed/t1XxeS-wVFA\" width=\"560\" height=\"315\" frameborder=\"0\"></iframe></p>\r\n<p class=\"embed-responsive embed-responsive-16by9\">Euan, Del, Tom and Ben AKA Human Nature.</p>\r\n<p><img id=\"blog_image_67\" class=\"center img-responsive\" src=\"/tt/tt.php?src=./uploads/hnposter.jpg&amp;w=940&amp;h=\" alt=\"\" /></p>','{\"category\":[\"2\"],\"tags\":[\"humannature\"],\"slug\":\"humannature\",\"heading\":\"Human Nature\"}','2024-12-11 12:53:17'),
(10,38,'<p>[blog-image:eyJpZCI6MTYsImJsb2dfaWQiOjM4LCJmaWxlbmFtZSI6IlVudGl0bGVkLTEuanBnIiwiaW1hZ2Vfd2lkdGgiOm51bGwsImltYWdlX2hlaWdodCI6bnVsbCwic2l6ZSI6IiIsImZsdWlkIjoiaW1nLWZsdWlkIiwiY2VudGVyZWQiOiIiLCJjYXB0aW9uIjoiIn0=]</p>','{\"category\":[\"5\"],\"tags\":[\"dignanporch\",\"greatescape\"],\"slug\":\"dignan\",\"heading\":\"dignan great escape\"}','2024-12-11 12:54:52'),
(11,38,'<p>[blog-image:eyJpZCI6MTYsImJsb2dfaWQiOjM4LCJmaWxlbmFtZSI6IlVudGl0bGVkLTEuanBnIiwiaW1hZ2Vfd2lkdGgiOm51bGwsImltYWdlX2hlaWdodCI6bnVsbCwic2l6ZSI6IiIsImZsdWlkIjoiaW1nLWZsdWlkIiwiY2VudGVyZWQiOiIiLCJjYXB0aW9uIjoiIn0=]</p>','{\"category\":[\"2\",\"5\"],\"tags\":[\"dignanporch\",\"greatescape\"],\"slug\":\"dignan\",\"heading\":\"dignan porch great escape\"}','2024-12-11 12:55:10'),
(12,33,'<p>[blog-image:eyJpZCI6MTEsImJsb2dfaWQiOjMzLCJmaWxlbmFtZSI6InRpbTIuanBnIiwiaW1hZ2Vfd2lkdGgiOm51bGwsImltYWdlX2hlaWdodCI6bnVsbCwic2l6ZSI6IiIsImZsdWlkIjoiaW1nLWZsdWlkIiwiY2VudGVyZWQiOiIiLCJjYXB0aW9uIjoiIn0=]<img id=\"blog_image_11\" class=\"center img-responsive\" src=\"/tt/tt.php?src=./uploads/tim2.jpg&amp;w=940&amp;h=\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p><a href=\"http://www.timothyedwardhill.com/\">Tim Hill</a> AKA <a href=\"http://bivouac1927.blogspot.co.uk/\">Bivouac 1927</a> AKA <a href=\"http://veilcraft.com/\">Veil Craft</a> is one of the most brilliantly creative people I\'ve ever known in my life. These images cost me a bomb today in petrol money, congestion charges, parking tickets and fines but I just don\'t care because it was too much fun just hanging out. &nbsp;Tim was very into discussing four-dimensional geometry with me today. (I didn\'t really have much to bring to the table.) &nbsp;I picked him up in south London (where we drank a quick coffee and had some cheese on toast - Tim also had some homemade marmalade) before visiting a random car breakers where Tim spotted a wrecked vintage Triumph automobile with a wooden-finish interior and token beaten up Bible on the dashboard, plus broomstick attached to the rear. &nbsp; We then headed north for spur of the moment Vietnamese food in Old St and then I dropped him off in Bethnal Green where he works as an artist\'s assistant.</p>\r\n<p>[blog-image:eyJpZCI6MTMsImJsb2dfaWQiOjMzLCJmaWxlbmFtZSI6InRpbTEuanBnIiwiaW1hZ2Vfd2lkdGgiOm51bGwsImltYWdlX2hlaWdodCI6bnVsbCwic2l6ZSI6IiIsImZsdWlkIjoiaW1nLWZsdWlkIiwiY2VudGVyZWQiOiIiLCJjYXB0aW9uIjoiIn0=]</p>\r\n<p>[blog-image:eyJpZCI6MTIsImJsb2dfaWQiOjMzLCJmaWxlbmFtZSI6InRpbTMuanBnIiwiaW1hZ2Vfd2lkdGgiOm51bGwsImltYWdlX2hlaWdodCI6bnVsbCwic2l6ZSI6IiIsImZsdWlkIjoiaW1nLWZsdWlkIiwiY2VudGVyZWQiOiIiLCJjYXB0aW9uIjoiIn0=]</p>','{\"category\":[\"5\"],\"tags\":[\"portraiture\"],\"slug\":\"tim\",\"heading\":\"Subject Tim\"}','2024-12-11 12:58:18'),
(13,32,'<p>[blog-image:eyJpZCI6OCwiYmxvZ19pZCI6MzIsImZpbGVuYW1lIjoibG92ZS5qcGciLCJpbWFnZV93aWR0aCI6bnVsbCwiaW1hZ2VfaGVpZ2h0IjpudWxsLCJzaXplIjoiIiwiZmx1aWQiOiJpbWctZmx1aWQiLCJjZW50ZXJlZCI6IiIsImNhcHRpb24iOiIifQ==]</p>\r\n<p>[blog-image:eyJpZCI6OSwiYmxvZ19pZCI6MzIsImZpbGVuYW1lIjoiY3JlZXBzLmpwZyIsImltYWdlX3dpZHRoIjpudWxsLCJpbWFnZV9oZWlnaHQiOm51bGwsInNpemUiOiIiLCJmbHVpZCI6ImltZy1mbHVpZCIsImNlbnRlcmVkIjoiIiwiY2FwdGlvbiI6IiJ9]</p>','{\"category\":[\"5\"],\"tags\":[\"strasbourg\"],\"slug\":\"strasbourg\",\"heading\":\"Strasbourg\"}','2024-12-11 13:01:28'),
(14,29,'<p>[blog-image:eyJpZCI6NCwiYmxvZ19pZCI6MjksImZpbGVuYW1lIjoibmV3aGF2ZW4uanBnIiwiaW1hZ2Vfd2lkdGgiOm51bGwsImltYWdlX2hlaWdodCI6bnVsbCwic2l6ZSI6IiIsImZsdWlkIjoiaW1nLWZsdWlkIiwiY2VudGVyZWQiOiIiLCJjYXB0aW9uIjoiIn0=]<img id=\"blog_image_4\" src=\"/tt/tt.php?src=./uploads/newhaven.jpg&amp;w=940&amp;h=\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p>Believe it or not there is no Photoshop sorcery going on with this photograph. A friend and I missioned from London to Newhaven (on the south coast) yesterday afternoon, for a late in the season dip in the ocean - perhaps the last opportunity to do so - when suddenly a huge cloud of sea fog engulfed us. I\'m pretty happy with how this one this image turned out.</p>','{\"category\":[\"5\"],\"tags\":[\"beach\",\"portraiture\"],\"slug\":\"newhaven\",\"heading\":\"Newhaven Haar\"}','2024-12-11 13:07:03'),
(15,21,'<pre>dpkg -l | grep dotdeb | awk \' { print ( $(2) ) }\' &gt; to_remove2<br /><br />apt-get remove $(cat &lt;to_remove2&gt;)</pre>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>','{\"category\":[\"1\"],\"tags\":[\"debian\",\"php\"],\"slug\":\"phpversionsdebian\",\"heading\":\"debian switching php versions\"}','2024-12-11 13:11:35'),
